*Predlažem* da odemo u bioskop. (I suggest we go to the movies.)

*Predložio* sam joj da odemo u restoran. (I suggested to her that we go to the restaurant.)

*Predlažem* da dijelimo troškove. (I suggest that we split the costs.)

*Predložila* sam profesoru da napravimo zajednički projekat. (I suggested to the professor that we do a joint project.)

*Predlog* je usvojen. (The proposal was accepted.)

*Predlagao* je da se održi sastanak. (He proposed that a meeting be held.)